            <span class="utterance" who="#michelsonV" start="1397.201" end="x">And in this way . . . ehh . . . I sustained myself until the instant when I met the first American division. And this first American division supplied me with dry [food] packages, and on these dry packages I managed to get to southern Bavaria to [the city of] <a class="placename" href="#vothL381">Kempten</a>.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
